<subSubSection pageId="150" pageNumber="548" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="150.[1443,2650,1162,1746]" pageId="150" pageNumber="548">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1444,1798,1556,1589]" pageId="150" pageNumber="548">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Endangered on The IUCN Red List. The Geata Mouse Shrew is rather rare in its small and fragmented distribution, where its habitat is continuing to decline in viability.
</paragraph>
